{"tid":2059742,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"傳奇 FPS 遊戲《Counter-Strike 1.6》正式開放透過瀏覽器免費遊玩","createTime":"2020-06-11T06:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T15:54:34.000Z","uid":1121,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcd4de8936bed6bc6291cabe188190e046317e0","tid":2059742,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:37:08.000Z","msg":"若說到 FPS（第一人稱射擊遊戲）遊戲史上最經典的作品，相信若《Counter-Strike》（譯：絕對武力系列）說第二，沒有其他遊戲會說自己是第一。在 2000 年首度問世，為當時的電玩界掀起一波前所未有的「槍戰」熱潮，挾帶的高漲的人氣除了 PC 平台之外，隨後推出的續作也紛紛登上了 PlayStation 3、Xbox 和 Xbox 360 等平台。不過在眾多作品之中，最讓人津津樂道的不外乎就是《Counter-Strike 1.6》了。<br />\n<br />\n為了讓眾多玩家更簡單回味懷舊經典，CS-ONLINE.CLUB 在歐洲、加拿大、美國、亞洲、印度和巴西皆設有服務器，正式開放《Counter-Strike 1.6》可透過網頁瀏覽器遊玩，玩家無須註冊帳號即可與朋友聯機對戰，而對於那些不想和隨機玩家對戰的用戶，CS-ONLINE.CLUB 也提供伺服器租賃，以提供更多的隱私並節省成本。最後也最重要的是，遊戲將完全免費。<br />\n<br />\n各位不妨前往 CS-ONLINE.CLUB，在瀏覽器上遊玩經典的反恐第一人稱射擊遊戲《Counter-Strike 1.6》，回憶一下過往的榮耀。"},{"pid":"caa45fb263b3aebc9c8487688ec61814759ec1fc","tid":2059742,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/6/play-counter-strike-1-6-on-browser-how-info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2020%2F6%2Fplay-counter-strike-1-6-on-browser-how-info&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRLnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=2bf85572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2020/6/play-counter-strike-1-6-on-browser-how-info</a>"},{"pid":"5c8a3a3b54ae590b4761c0fa0592c0cd220fe2d1","tid":2059742,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:40:21.000Z","msg":"上唔到<br />\n你地上到冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010695a5c91309d6b9fbe6ed24167d72d8c93dde","tid":2059742,"uid":315359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T